WEBVTT

00:00:01.520 --> 00:00:05.510
Breathe upon me, breath of God.

00:00:05.520 --> 00:00:07.830
Breathe upon me,

00:00:07.840 --> 00:00:10.790
Spirit of the Lord.

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:12.790
Father, I thank you for this time of

00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:14.830
prayer tonight.

00:00:14.840 --> 00:00:17.150
Father, we have work to do, and I yield

00:00:17.160 --> 00:00:19.470
