00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:25.270
you.

00:00:25.280 --> 00:00:27.750
I thank you, Father, that we yield.

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:31.150
We yield to the precious Holy Spirit,

00:00:31.160 --> 00:00:33.350
