00:00:39.960 --> 00:00:42.350
All glory to Jesus.

00:00:42.360 --> 00:00:46.630
We give all the glory to Jesus

00:00:46.640 --> 00:00:50.190
and tell of his love, his wonderful

00:00:50.200 --> 00:00:56.430
love. We give all of the glory to Jesus

00:00:56.440 --> 00:01:00.590
