00:31:21.920 --> 00:31:23.990
I'll back it.'So that's where it started

00:31:24.000 --> 00:31:26.990
from. But he got so tired of sowing in

00:31:27.000 --> 00:31:28.950
the offering

00:31:28.960 --> 00:31:32.030
and waiting for a miracle always,

00:31:32.030 --> 00:31:32.040
and

00:31:32.040 --> 00:31:35.150
instead he said, 'Whatever you do, I'll

00:31:35.160 --> 00:31:37.430
give you power to get wealth. You go out

00:31:37.440 --> 00:31:40.590
and make it happen, Captain. Stop

00:31:40.600 --> 00:31:44.150
waiting for a

00:31:44.150 --> 00:31:44.160
handout.'It's

00:31:44.160 --> 00:31:45.470
like this, you know,

00:31:45.480 --> 00:31:47.630
when people say, 'Teach a

00:31:47.640 --> 00:31:49.710
person to fish.

00:31:49.720 --> 00:31:51.510
If you give somebody a

00:31:51.520 --> 00:31:53.150
fish, they'll have enough for a day. If

00:31:53.160 --> 00:31:54.510
you teach a person to fish, they'll be

00:31:54.520 --> 00:31:56.070
able to feed themselves

00:31:56.070 --> 00:31:56.080
forever,'you

00:31:56.080 --> 00:31:57.470
know, kind of a deal.

00:31:57.480 --> 00:31:59.110
I probably butchered that, but it's

00:31:59.120 --> 00:32:01.590
similar. But I'm trying to tell

00:32:01.600 --> 00:32:03.030
you all,

00:32:03.040 --> 00:32:06.150
out of desperation,

00:32:06.160 --> 00:32:09.990
doing eBay, Poshmark, and Mercari

00:32:10.000 --> 00:32:13.710
changed our life. But we didn't wait

00:32:13.720 --> 00:32:15.510
for it to happen; we went out and took

00:32:15.520 --> 00:32:16.830
what's ours.

00:32:16.840 --> 00:32:19.350
We learned to go to thrift

00:32:19.360 --> 00:32:23.350
stores. It took us forever.

00:32:23.360 --> 00:32:26.150
Diana and me, praying in the spirit

00:32:26.160 --> 00:32:28.270
for hours and

00:32:28.270 --> 00:32:28.280
hours—that's

00:32:28.280 --> 00:32:32.470
where I learned to develop my gift.

00:32:32.480 --> 00:32:37.190
But it was out of desperation,

00:32:37.200 --> 00:32:40.310
and I would learn where to go,

00:32:40.320 --> 00:32:41.950
asking the Father, 'Show me where the

00:32:41.960 --> 00:32:43.710
good stuff is. I'm looking for something

00:32:43.710 --> 00:32:43.720
that

00:32:43.720 --> 00:32:45.830
sells for

00:32:45.830 --> 00:32:45.840
more.'So,

00:32:45.840 --> 00:32:48.470
just praying in the spirit,

00:32:48.480 --> 00:32:50.950
and eBay changed our life. The

00:32:50.960 --> 00:32:52.510
Holy Spirit

00:32:52.520 --> 00:32:54.710
used that to change our life.

00:32:54.720 --> 00:32:57.910
And it was to the point where,

00:32:57.920 --> 00:33:00.470
in the first six months, we made more

00:33:00.480 --> 00:33:02.350
money than we made an entire year at

00:33:02.360 --> 00:33:04.590
the church.

00:33:04.600 --> 00:33:06.950
And it started compounding. We just

00:33:06.960 --> 00:33:09.230
kept growing and kept doing it. But I

00:33:09.240 --> 00:33:11.390
want to tell you, I got so tired of

00:33:11.400 --> 00:33:12.230
the—wow,

00:33:12.240 --> 00:33:14.669
I wonder what that's all about.

00:33:14.679 --> 00:33:16.070
You hear those, please.

00:33:18.679 --> 00:33:21.790
I got so tired of

00:33:21.800 --> 00:33:24.030
the prosperity preaching

00:33:24.040 --> 00:33:25.950
at church.

00:33:25.960 --> 00:33:29.550
A lot of charismatic, 'Sow your $58

00:33:29.550 --> 00:33:29.560
seed'—not

00:33:29.560 --> 00:33:31.669
that I'm knocking that,

00:33:31.679 --> 00:33:32.830
man—'Sow

00:33:32.840 --> 00:33:35.550
your 58 for your $58

00:33:35.550 --> 00:33:35.560
miracle.'I'm

00:33:35.560 --> 00:33:37.350
very careful; I don't touch the

00:33:37.360 --> 00:33:38.510
anointing.

00:33:38.520 --> 00:33:40.990
But I got tired of hearing it and not

00:33:41.000 --> 00:33:43.150
seeing the fruit of it, and always not

00:33:43.160 --> 00:33:45.350
putting my boat into motion.

00:33:45.360 --> 00:33:47.790
And so I tell you all this because

00:33:47.800 --> 00:33:49.669
I think it gets real flaky there. There's

00:33:49.679 --> 00:33:51.910
a real flakiness to it.

00:33:51.920 --> 00:33:54.110
I asked God, 'Show me how to flip

00:33:54.120 --> 00:33:55.550
a car.'So

00:33:55.550 --> 00:33:55.560
I'd

00:33:55.560 --> 00:33:57.550
find a car

00:33:57.560 --> 00:33:58.950
that was

00:33:58.960 --> 00:34:02.190
on another part of town,

00:34:02.200 --> 00:34:04.950
try to find it for a cheap

00:34:04.960 --> 00:34:06.030
deal—800

00:34:06.040 --> 00:34:07.070
bucks—and

00:34:07.080 --> 00:34:08.590
try to flip

00:34:08.600 --> 00:34:10.630
it.

00:34:10.640 --> 00:34:12.149
Put a little bit of money—it might be a

00:34:12.159 --> 00:34:13.869
clunker that's broken—put a little bit

00:34:13.879 --> 00:34:15.590
of money into it, clean it up real good, put

00:34:15.600 --> 00:34:17.389
some new tires on it. Maybe they're used,

00:34:17.389 --> 00:34:17.399
because

00:34:17.399 --> 00:34:18.790
I always look for used tires.

00:34:18.800 --> 00:34:20.389
You can find some tires that

00:34:20.399 --> 00:34:21.869
were not too treaded out. I don't know

00:34:21.879 --> 00:34:22.669
why I'm telling you, but there's

00:34:22.669 --> 00:34:22.679
some

00:34:22.679 --> 00:34:24.869
for somebody

00:34:24.879 --> 00:34:27.510
trying to figure out how to double and

00:34:27.520 --> 00:34:28.950
triple your money,

00:34:28.960 --> 00:34:30.510
asking the Holy Spirit to give you

00:34:30.520 --> 00:34:33.149
wisdom about it,

00:34:33.159 --> 00:34:34.869
do you know what I'm saying?

00:34:34.879 --> 00:34:37.310
Not waiting for

00:34:37.320 --> 00:34:39.790
somebody always to hand you a Holy

00:34:39.800 --> 00:34:41.470
Ghost handshake.

00:34:41.480 --> 00:34:42.909
'Here, brother, here's your

00:34:42.909 --> 00:34:42.919
$100.'You're

00:34:42.919 --> 00:34:45.149
going, 'Oh my God, thank God I got $100,

00:34:45.159 --> 00:34:48.030
that'll get me through two

00:34:48.030 --> 00:34:48.040
days.'And

00:34:48.040 --> 00:34:49.669
you're going, 'Oh God, I've got to

00:34:49.669 --> 00:34:49.679
believe

00:34:49.679 --> 00:34:51.630
for the next

00:34:51.630 --> 00:34:51.640
one.'But

00:34:51.640 --> 00:34:54.030
believing God for so much more

00:34:54.040 --> 00:34:55.590
than always just waiting for your Holy

00:34:55.600 --> 00:34:57.830
Ghost handshake at church.

00:34:57.840 --> 00:34:58.590
You know what I'm talking

00:34:58.590 --> 00:34:58.600
about—Holy

00:34:58.600 --> 00:34:59.830
Ghost handshake. You're looking for

00:34:59.830 --> 00:34:59.840
a

00:34:59.840 --> 00:35:01.630
sister with a lot of money. And a

00:35:01.640 --> 00:35:02.990
lot of times you see the ministry of

00:35:03.000 --> 00:35:04.790
hints. You're walking around going,

00:35:04.800 --> 00:35:06.630
'Well, I'm believing God for my

00:35:06.640 --> 00:35:07.950
electric bill today,'and you're talking

00:35:07.960 --> 00:35:09.710
to the rich people at church, hoping

00:35:09.720 --> 00:35:11.870
they'll have sympathy on you,

00:35:11.880 --> 00:35:12.910
that they'll want to help pay your

00:35:12.920 --> 00:35:14.830
electric bill because you're going, 'Oh God,

00:35:14.840 --> 00:35:17.270
you know, we've been struggling.

00:35:17.280 --> 00:35:18.830
You know, we're believing God just like

00:35:18.830 --> 00:35:18.840
everybody.'And

00:35:18.840 --> 00:35:20.470
you look at them,

00:35:20.480 --> 00:35:22.190
they're going, 'Okay, well, I know what

00:35:22.200 --> 00:35:23.430
you're doing. You're asking for money in

00:35:23.440 --> 00:35:26.910
a polite Christianese

00:35:26.910 --> 00:35:26.920
way.'I

00:35:26.920 --> 00:35:29.070
didn't want to be that.

00:35:29.080 --> 00:35:30.510
I wanted to be the man with a

00:35:30.510 --> 00:35:30.520
picture

00:35:30.520 --> 00:35:32.550
in his hand.

00:35:32.560 --> 00:35:34.190
Teach me.

00:35:34.200 --> 00:35:35.910
Teach me to not fish with just a

00:35:35.920 --> 00:35:38.190
fishing pole. Teach me to fish with a

00:35:38.200 --> 00:35:39.550
net,

00:35:39.560 --> 00:35:41.910
Father. Teach me.

00:35:41.920 --> 00:35:44.230
And that's why I continually am asking

00:35:44.240 --> 00:35:46.670
the Father, and when I hear about

00:35:46.670 --> 00:35:46.680
Magdala

00:35:46.680 --> 00:35:49.310
and these projects—and I think

00:35:49.320 --> 00:35:51.470
it's like $20 million to finish this

00:35:51.480 --> 00:35:54.190
project, it's huge money,

00:35:54.190 --> 00:35:54.200
right?—and

00:35:54.200 --> 00:35:58.830
I go, 'That should not be.

00:35:58.840 --> 00:36:00.150
The body of Christ should be the head,

00:36:00.160 --> 00:36:02.349
not the tail, above and not

00:36:02.349 --> 00:36:02.359
beneath.'But

00:36:02.359 --> 00:36:04.990
I think a lot of the times because it is

00:36:05.000 --> 00:36:07.030
Satan's wheelhouse, and he tries to block

00:36:07.040 --> 00:36:08.910
the blessing from the body of Christ so

00:36:08.920 --> 00:36:11.190
much because he knows what it's going

00:36:11.200 --> 00:36:12.510
to take to get the gospel out, because

00:36:12.520 --> 00:36:14.710
why? It's all about souls.

00:36:14.720 --> 00:36:16.390
The more we have the money, the more we

00:36:16.400 --> 00:36:18.430
have the finances, we're able to get the

00:36:18.440 --> 00:36:21.750
job done so we can get out of here.

00:36:21.760 --> 00:36:23.870
But if you're broke, you can't even give

00:36:23.880 --> 00:36:25.230
enough. It's like the youth project at

00:36:25.240 --> 00:36:26.390
the church trying to finish the rest of

00:36:26.400 --> 00:36:28.430
that. I think they need another,

00:36:28.440 --> 00:36:31.910
like, $200,000 or something more.

00:36:31.920 --> 00:36:33.150
So,

00:36:33.160 --> 00:36:35.230
if you're in a small community, $200,000

00:36:35.230 --> 00:36:35.240
is

00:36:35.240 --> 00:36:37.150
a lot of money. Do you get that?

00:36:37.160 --> 00:36:38.670
So you get a little bit here, you get a

00:36:38.680 --> 00:36:39.950
little bit there, and you're excited

00:36:39.960 --> 00:36:41.510
whenever you get enough to be

00:36:41.520 --> 00:36:43.349
able to put some cement slabs up or

00:36:43.359 --> 00:36:45.630
whatever. But I thought, what does

00:36:45.630 --> 00:36:45.640
it

00:36:45.640 --> 00:36:48.910
take to be a paymaster?

00:36:48.920 --> 00:36:51.510
What does it take to be that

00:36:51.520 --> 00:36:54.230
person that has the big money,

00:36:54.240 --> 00:36:56.270
like the Greens? If it

00:36:56.280 --> 00:36:59.190
wasn't for the Greens of Hobby Lobby,

00:36:59.200 --> 00:37:01.390
ORU wouldn't exist right now.

00:37:01.400 --> 00:37:03.550
The Holy Spirit used them. And some people

00:37:03.560 --> 00:37:05.349
get ticked off at people being, you know,

00:37:05.359 --> 00:37:06.790
they say, 'F the rich'and all this

00:37:06.800 --> 00:37:09.510
craziness, whatever. I mean,

00:37:09.520 --> 00:37:11.630
it's so ignorant.

00:37:11.640 --> 00:37:14.110
If it wasn't for the Greens

00:37:14.120 --> 00:37:16.790
being used by the Holy Spirit, ORU would

00:37:16.800 --> 00:37:18.430
have closed their doors. I think they

00:37:18.440 --> 00:37:21.590
had to give them $47 million

00:37:21.600 --> 00:37:22.510
or they would have closed their doors

00:37:22.520 --> 00:37:24.630
because of mismanagement of money.

00:37:24.640 --> 00:37:26.470
There had to be something,

00:37:26.480 --> 00:37:29.750
but it was them bailing them out that

00:37:29.760 --> 00:37:31.470
God used to help save that whole

00:37:31.480 --> 00:37:34.150
university. And my wife graduated there,

00:37:34.160 --> 00:37:36.110
thank God.

00:37:36.120 --> 00:37:37.630
Thank God, it is a Christian university.

00:37:37.640 --> 00:37:39.190
They're changing lives. But the Lord

00:37:39.200 --> 00:37:40.910
showed me a major revival is about to

00:37:40.920 --> 00:37:42.990
happen there.

00:37:43.000 --> 00:37:45.430
But it took somebody with some common

00:37:45.440 --> 00:37:47.830
sense that had 400 stores, Hobby Lobbies,

00:37:47.840 --> 00:37:49.950
and Mardel's all throughout the United

00:37:49.960 --> 00:37:52.150
States that was able to say, 'Here, here's

00:37:52.160 --> 00:37:54.830
a $47 million

00:37:54.830 --> 00:37:54.840
check.'I

00:37:54.840 --> 00:37:56.270
don't know about you, but even a

00:37:56.270 --> 00:37:56.280
million-dollar

00:37:56.280 --> 00:37:57.430
check, I'd pass out.

00:37:57.440 --> 00:37:59.430
$100,000, you know, come on.

00:37:59.440 --> 00:38:01.430
But 47 million bucks

00:38:01.440 --> 00:38:03.430
here,

00:38:03.440 --> 00:38:05.430
do you—that

00:38:05.430 --> 00:38:05.440
is an

00:38:05.440 --> 00:38:08.790
absurd amount of money.

00:38:08.800 --> 00:38:11.390
That's crazy money. But they had

00:38:11.400 --> 00:38:13.390
it,

00:38:13.400 --> 00:38:15.230
and I thought we need more

00:38:15.240 --> 00:38:16.710
people like that. But what is it going

00:38:16.720 --> 00:38:19.070
to take to get that? First, the love of

00:38:19.080 --> 00:38:20.670
money is the root of all evil. If you're

00:38:20.680 --> 00:38:22.070
crazy about money and God can't get it

00:38:22.080 --> 00:38:24.430
through you, He won't get it to you.

00:38:24.440 --> 00:38:26.070
So, I really truly believe there's

00:38:26.080 --> 00:38:27.830
something more to this for the

00:38:27.830 --> 00:38:27.840
end-time

00:38:27.840 --> 00:38:29.790
harvest and the end-time wealth transfer

00:38:29.800 --> 00:38:32.110
for what we need for these next couple

00:38:32.120 --> 00:38:33.430
of months and going into the next

00:38:33.440 --> 00:38:35.750
year. I heard one pastor talking about

00:38:35.750 --> 00:38:35.760
how

00:38:35.760 --> 00:38:37.550
we're about to have

00:38:37.560 --> 00:38:39.750
an economic crisis. I believe there's

00:38:39.760 --> 00:38:41.910
an outpouring of finances first. And

00:38:41.920 --> 00:38:43.630
that's what I believe for the body of

00:38:43.640 --> 00:38:46.630
Christ, that we lack nothing.

00:38:46.640 --> 00:38:49.030
We should not be lacking anything. We

00:38:49.040 --> 00:38:52.910
need this to get the job done.

00:38:52.920 --> 00:38:54.870
So, I think about things all the

00:38:54.880 --> 00:38:56.030
time.

00:38:56.040 --> 00:38:57.550
I pray and the Lord gives me these

00:38:57.560 --> 00:38:59.310
ideas. I'm driving down the road and

00:38:59.320 --> 00:39:00.190
He'll say, 'That

00:39:00.200 --> 00:39:01.830
land over there. If

00:39:01.840 --> 00:39:03.670
somebody buys that, they'll be able to,

00:39:03.680 --> 00:39:04.950
and within the next couple of months, that

00:39:04.960 --> 00:39:06.190
land's going to

00:39:06.200 --> 00:39:08.110
quadruple in price and it'd be worth

00:39:10.070 --> 00:39:10.080
millions.'But

00:39:11.760 --> 00:39:12.990
that takes money to buy that. But

00:39:13.000 --> 00:39:15.670
He's always educating me.

00:39:15.680 --> 00:39:18.190
He's always teaching me about the

00:39:18.190 --> 00:39:18.200
end-time

00:39:18.200 --> 00:39:20.710
harvest money. He teaches me

00:39:20.720 --> 00:39:23.150
all the time and He talks to me, and I

00:39:23.160 --> 00:39:24.750
know something's about to happen. I

00:39:24.760 --> 00:39:26.470
know. I just believe it

00:39:26.470 --> 00:39:26.480
because

00:39:26.480 --> 00:39:27.510
I'm like, 'Why are you telling me

00:39:27.520 --> 00:39:30.430
this stuff? Are you just educating

00:39:30.430 --> 00:39:30.440
me?'Practicing

00:39:30.440 --> 00:39:32.310
His presence—people go,

00:39:32.320 --> 00:39:33.390
'What's that mean, Brandon? What does that

00:39:33.400 --> 00:39:36.110
mean to practice His

00:39:36.110 --> 00:39:36.120
presence?'Act

00:39:36.120 --> 00:39:40.349
like He's there.

00:39:40.359 --> 00:39:42.670
I don't look at God as twinkle, twinkle,

00:39:42.680 --> 00:39:44.230
little star. 'Lord, you're way out there

00:39:44.240 --> 00:39:45.910
somewhere where you

00:39:45.910 --> 00:39:45.920
are.'He's

00:39:45.920 --> 00:39:49.150
in me. He dwells. As He is, so are we

00:39:49.160 --> 00:39:51.630
in this world. I act like He's just like

00:39:51.640 --> 00:39:54.630
my wife sitting next to me.

00:39:54.640 --> 00:39:56.670
'Hey, how's your day?

00:39:56.680 --> 00:39:58.150
I love you.

00:39:58.160 --> 00:39:59.830
I want to talk to you. Are you my

00:39:59.840 --> 00:40:01.030
friend?'When

00:40:01.040 --> 00:40:02.790
I told you I ticked Him off

00:40:02.800 --> 00:40:05.110
yesterday, I knew it immediately because my

00:40:05.120 --> 00:40:07.150
broadcast was terrible.

00:40:07.160 --> 00:40:09.270
And I said, 'Lord, why is this so

00:40:09.270 --> 00:40:09.280
bad?'He

00:40:09.280 --> 00:40:12.350
said, 'Your attitude's bad,

00:40:12.360 --> 00:40:14.230
and I'm not going to pour that

00:40:14.240 --> 00:40:16.670
cloak on you. It's teaching you.

00:40:16.680 --> 00:40:19.350
You cannot have that. You've got to

00:40:19.360 --> 00:40:21.750
repent and go on.'And the moment I fixed

00:40:21.760 --> 00:40:24.830
it—but

00:40:24.840 --> 00:40:27.150
it caused me to align

00:40:27.150 --> 00:40:27.160
because,

00:40:27.160 --> 00:40:28.790
bottom line, folks, I was

00:40:28.800 --> 00:40:30.390
irritated because there were so many of

00:40:30.400 --> 00:40:32.030
you all irritated that came to the

00:40:32.040 --> 00:40:33.550
meeting that wanted to talk to me and I

00:40:33.560 --> 00:40:35.150
didn't know how to handle it, and there

00:40:35.150 --> 00:40:35.160
were

00:40:35.160 --> 00:40:36.270
things that I had to deal with in

00:40:36.270 --> 00:40:36.280
my heart

00:40:36.280 --> 00:40:38.670
about it.

00:40:38.680 --> 00:40:40.830
And the Lord instructed me

00:40:40.840 --> 00:40:42.550
because I didn't know what to do.

00:40:42.560 --> 00:40:44.630
I'm new at this. I'm just a dude that's

00:40:44.640 --> 00:40:47.270
just getting raised up in ministry,

00:40:47.280 --> 00:40:49.350
and I'm just telling you all, I

00:40:49.360 --> 00:40:50.830
don't have all the answers and I'm

00:40:50.840 --> 00:40:52.190
asking the Holy Spirit, 'You teach me. I

00:40:52.200 --> 00:40:55.110
need you. I don't know what to

00:40:55.110 --> 00:40:55.120
do.'And

00:40:55.120 --> 00:40:57.830
as I grow, and I've seen my elders,

00:40:57.840 --> 00:40:59.390
you know, that have been in this for 50

